Name: The Conners
Title: Who Are Bosses, Boats and Eckhart Tolle?
Desc: Chuck's new purchase of a boat creates a rift; Darlene hires her first assistant.
LongDescription: Chuck's new purchase of a boat creates a rift; Darlene hires her first assistant at Wellman's Plastics but soon realizes she is anything but helpful; Jackie is laser-focused on her dream of being a contestant on "Jeopardy!"
